<p class="formnote">Uploaded images will be resized to suit. If you want to associated several images with a source document, the best way is to illustrate its fragments.</p>

<p>
  <label for="<%= item.class.to_s.downcase %>_image">Upload an image: <%= file_column_field item.class.to_s.downcase, "image" %></label>
  <% if item.has_image? %><br /><a class="pale" href="<%= url_for_file_column(item.class.to_s.downcase, "image", "preview") %>" rel="lightbox"><%= image_tag(url_for_file_column(item.class.to_s.downcase, "image", "thumb"), :size => "18x18", :alt => '') %>
  current image is <%= item.image_relative_path %></a><% end %>
</p>
